  "description": "Property LocationWith a stay at Ho'olei Villas at Grand Wailea in Kihei (Wailea), you'll be within a 10-minute walk of Wailea Beach and Shops at Wailea. This beach resort is 21.1 mi (33.9 km) from Haleakala National Park and 0.8 mi (1.2 km) from Ulua Beach Park.\n\nDistances are displayed to the nearest 0.1 mile and kilometer. \n \nShops at Wailea - 0.5 km / 0.3 mi \n Wailea Beach - 0.7 km / 0.4 mi \n Wailea Blue Golf Course - 1.2 km / 0.7 mi \n Ulua Beach Park - 1.2 km / 0.8 mi \n Wailea Shopping Village Shopping Center - 1.3 km / 0.8 mi \n Ulua Beach - 1.5 km / 0.9 mi \n Polo Beach - 1.6 km / 1 mi \n Mokapu Beach - 1.8 km / 1.1 mi \n Palauea Beach - 1.8 km / 1.1 mi \n Po'olenalena Beach - 2.3 km / 1.4 mi \n Keawakapu Beach South - 2.7 km / 1.7 mi \n Wailea Gold Golf Course - 3 km / 1.9 mi \n Wailea Emerald Golf Course - 3 km / 1.9 mi \n Keawakapu Beach North - 3.1 km / 1.9 mi \n Chang's Beach - 3.2 km / 2 mi \n \nThe nearest airports are:\nKahului Airport (OGG) - 26.7 km / 16.6 mi\n West Maui Airport (JHM) - 55.4 km / 34.4 mi\n Hana, HI (HNM) - 100.7 km / 62.6 mi\n \n\nRoomsMake yourself at home in one of the 60 guestrooms, featuring kitchens with refrigerators and ovens. Rooms have private lanais. Wired and wireless internet access is complimentary, and LCD televisions with premium TV channels provide entertainment. Bathrooms with separate bathtubs and showers feature deep soaking bathtubs and designer toiletries.\n\nDining\nEnjoy a meal at the restaurant or snacks in the resort's coffee shop/cafe. Unwind at the end of the day with a drink at the bar/lounge or the swim-up bar. Continental breakfasts are served on weekdays from 7:00 AM to 10:30 AM for a fee.\n\nBusiness, Other Amenities \nFeatured amenities include a business center, limo/town car service, and complimentary newspapers in the lobby. Planning an event in Kihei? This resort has facilities measuring 99997 square feet (9290 square meters), including conference space.",
